{"tid":2417718,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中學校長會統計去年下半年中學生因移民海外升學而退學數字急升5成 教師離職人數亦增1成5","createTime":"2021-02-22T06:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T06:19:12.000Z","uid":292499,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"618aabb7a9d24dba26e30992755f387f37955781","tid":2417718,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:07:38.000Z","msg":"【學生移民海外升學大增5成  老師離職增15%  中學校長會:籲教局減干預給自主】 <br />\n...<br />\n在2020年7至11月，各中學共有1474名學生退學，2019年同期則有1195名學生退學，增加23%。調查進一步分析學生退學的原因，去年7至11月共有723名學生因為離港（包括移民和到海外升學）而退學，較2019年的475人大增5成。<br />\n<br />\n調查亦統計了教師除退休外的離職情況，在2020年7至11月，各中學共有235名教師離職，較2019年同期的205人增加15%。<br />\n<br />\n調查結果顯示，逾8成中學校長預期學生退學數字在未來會持續上升，亦有逾7成中學校長估計教師離職數字會繼續增加。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AKR1tiw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKR1tiw.png&h=3e825e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1391977291145676/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366243453719070%2Fposts%2F1391977291145676%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY%2FFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=578307df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1391977291145676/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"88403867c237c7f06a10424bd124b853151bf994","tid":2417718,"uid":292499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"疫情下都急升5成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b49d5e0030cdcce13e86c611a23c616c809f829","tid":2417718,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/